
How to compile:

1. Run ./configure --host=powerpc64-ps3-elf --enable-static --disable-shared 
2. Run make

How to install:
1. Copy the include folder to /usr/local/ps3dev/portlibs/ppu/include and rename it to SDL2
2. Copy the contents of build/.libs to /usr/local/ps3dev/portlibs/ppu/lib
3. Copy sdl2-config to /usr/local/ps3dev/portlibs/ppu/lib/pkgconfig/

Linking the library:
Use sdl2-config
